###
PUT http://localhost:4000/author-api/articles
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "articleId":"69b50cac263e13ab3439fbb1",
    "title":"article-1 by author 1",
    "category":"AI",
    "contents":"test article on AI"

}


### Delete article by Article ID (soft delete)
###can be restored by setting isArticleActive:false

PATCH http://localhost:4000/author-api/articles
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "articleId":"69b50cac263e13ab3439fbb1",
    "isArticleActive":true
}